'''''Look Magazine''''' is an art magazine of the Art Gallery Society of New South Wales in [[Australia]] since October 1985. The magazine is delivered to the members of the art gallery and is published on a monthly basis.<ref>{{cite web|title=Look magazine|url=http://www.artgallery.nsw.gov.au/members/become-a-member/benefits-of-membership/look-magazine/|work=Art Gallery NSW|accessdate=10 November 2015}}</ref>

